---
title: Garlic and Herb-Dressed Steak  with Heirloom Tomato Salad
description: A herbaceous heirloom tomato and pear salad with chives, lemon zest and goat cheese is the perfect accompaniment for luxurious, melt-in-your-mouth sirloin steaks. This premium weeknight meal is one for the 'gram!

